  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of magnesium sulphate on
      neostigmine-induced reversal of neuromuscular block by rocuronium
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of reversa time by neostigmine in magnesium group and control group
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
